# No local secrets are needed anymore.
#
# server.js is a static dev server only. All secrets live as Supabase Edge
# Function secrets (Dashboard → Edge Functions → Secrets, or `supabase secrets set`):
#   OPENAI_API_KEY            — used by the ai-import Edge Function
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY — auto-injected into Edge Functions by Supabase
#
# Never commit real keys. Rotate any key that has ever been committed.
